Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H1E2F95&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And how is the new virus\Nculture coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's developing incredibly fast.\NI've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I have to know. Just\Nwhat is this new virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is keep your\Nhead down and work on the vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the pathogen is as dreadful as it seems, we\Ncan't test it on humans until the vaccine is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Test it on humans...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Anyway, Sawada, how many vaccine samples have you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...About twenty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's not many, and\Nthe experiment starts soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you really intend\Nto test it on humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need you to be on\Nhand when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But... to be used like a guinea pig...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't imagine anyone volunteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!\NIt's GOD's Cat Monster Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dreary night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a cat doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Why the emergency call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat killed your mother? Kaori,\Ndid you have another bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream!\NIt was real, honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright. Why don't you show\Nme? Come on, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaori?\NWhy are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like she had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She said you'd been killed by a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed by a cat...? Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened to you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what do you want!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the human test\Nwas a success, Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of GOD's monsters, Cattius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you become a cat-man, you'll be\Na big help to GOD's Cat Monster Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment to turn humans\Ninto cat monsters is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! You will help cultivate\Nthe Cat Monster Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now to make this girl one of us--\N-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD... Just what are\Nyou plotting this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Run for it, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tachibana! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,M'still sleepy... What's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a little favour. Can we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's after this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee shop's too public, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we hide out here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but only 'cos she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-You don't mind, right, Chiko?\N-Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here's your tea.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, where'd you get that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a GOD monster turned\Nher folks into cat-people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat-people...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To cut a long story short... Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I wonder what they look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat-people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They got to you guys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, everyone in this\Napartment block is a cat-person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you'll be joining them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Run as soon as you see a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Cattius!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just keep\Nyour eyes shut tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I sink my infectious claws into your\Nbody, you'll become a cat-person too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori. Your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't really\Nturned into monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just... sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll help them get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So keep your spirits\Nup, and try to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the cat-people\Nfrom that apartment block go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are this girl's\Nparents being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cat Monster Plan isn't\Nprogressing steadily enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten or twenty cat-people\Nwon't accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The virus culture's been stalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Sawada resisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't cooperate\Nno matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you turned\Nhim into a cat-person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That just made his brain cat-like\Ntoo. He can't do his job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then turn him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This vaccine can\Nreturn your human forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, then\Nfollow orders and work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell right into\Nour trap, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is what you want,\Nyou'll have to face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your move, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! This will turn\Nyou back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kaori!\N-Kaori, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just\Ndreamt I was a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysteries of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! I'll pay\Nhim back for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's horrific Cat Monster\NPlan has been foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But this has only deepened\NApollo Geist's hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, don't let\Nyour guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(12,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's monster Occultos plunges the citizens\Nof Tokyo into despair with his Ghost Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Toubeh and the gang infiltrate a\Nhaunted house, where a dark trap awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Corpses Call from the Haunted House!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
